features: Stress Free Traveling: Enthralled by travel, yet frazzled by packing chaos? Introduce packing cubes to your travel gear. They help sort, organize, and locate items quickly. Say goodbye to misplaced valuables and the frustration of unpacking for one item. It's time to enhance your journey with effortless organization!

The Right Materials: Our packing cubes boast a 26% superior thickness. After comprehensive analysis of other luggage organizers, we found their 230D Polyester or various polyester fabrics lacking. In contrast, we've chosen to create our travel bags with 290D Polyester - a fabric significantly more robust and resilient, promising the longevity and durability you need for everyday use.

Seamless and Reliable Zippers: Our packing cubes feature sturdy metal, two-way zippers that effortlessly glide, minimizing jamming and snags. Designed for long-lasting performance, even with frequent use, ensuring hassle-free packing and unpacking every time.

Discover the Open Eva Advantage: With breathable and see-through mesh panels, your items stay fresh and easily visible. With Eva, you are able to clearly see your items and know which cube has the contents you are looking for. Enjoy hassle-free access and keep everything organized effortlessly.

Versatile Travel Organizer Bag: Whether you are carrying an airline carry-on suitcase, duffle bag, backpack, or tote, these packing bags are sure to fit compactly without taking up a lot of space. You can take these travel cubes for packing on business trips, camping adventures, and vacations, to keep your clothes, toiletries, and other accessories separated, or also use them at home as storage organizers for your cabinets to keep your closet spick-and-span.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Awesome set to make packing a breeze
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this item to help with organizing my packing for international travel. I was very pleased with my purchase and the different sizes offered in the item. I found these items very durable and of good quality. They were very easy to use and pack and was a great tool to keep my closet organized. The only thing I did not like about the item was the size of the dirty clothes bag. I would have liked a larger bag to accommodate the dirty clothes I acquire during my trip. But overall, this was a great purchase and will be used for all future travel.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 5, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Ordered this for traveling, and I keep it in my duffle bag. I love the pale pink color, and it really worked out well on my last trip. I was able to keep all my clothes well organized throughout the trip. They are easy to store in drawers at the hotel, and they make packing up to leave much less stressful as long as you keep your stuff in the cubes. They keep your clothes neater because you can roll up your pants, shirts, etc. I also liked the laundry bag it came with. They are a decent size and if you roll up your clothes and pack and organize them carefully, they will fit a lot. They fit at least 6 days worth of clothes for me. The material was also very good. Highly recommended.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars WOW! GAME CHANGER!!
reviews.reviewText: We used these for an 8 day trip to the Bahamas. I packed all of my clothes in them. I used the S, M and L cubes. I didn't need the XL, because I didn't take bulky sweaters or jackets. I also didn't use the shoe bag because I like to wrap my shoes individually. And, because I took 7 pairs, including 2 sets of heels, so it wasn't practical bc they didn't fit and I didn't want the flip flops all over my white sneakers. The pics show my stuff when we got back. I wish I would have taken pics before we left to show how perfectly neat these cubes held all my clothes. In the pics, the L bag is half empty, so I rolled it up to position it next to the other 2 cubes on the trip home. The laundry bag is big enough to hold 9 changes of clothes (no jeans, but 1 jean shorts). So, what you see next to the empty pink bag was everything else that fit in the 3 half empty cubes in the suit case. The suit case is 27" long, 18" wide and 10" deep. When the cubes are full, they are pretty heavy, approx 5 to 10 lbs, depending on the size of the cube. I will never travel w/o these cubes. My clothes were organized and stayed exactly how I packed them. And, when 1 of our suitcases got too heavy, it was sooo easy to transfer the cubes around between the 2 big suit cases and 2 carry-ons. Last year, we went to Cancun with the kids, before we bought a suit case weighing device, we had to open all of our suitcases in the middle of the PACKED airport, trying to shift the weight around between 6 suitcases, grabbing random clothes. There were underwear flying around all over the place! It was awful! Now, all we have to do is weigh, rearrange if necessary, and go. Now, at the hotel, the cubes went into the drawers and my clean clothes never touched the hotel drawers. So, when I got home, the unused clothes were completely separate from the used clothes, they were perfectly clean and I didn't have to wash EVERYTHING (used & unused, like I usually do). My husband didn't want to use all of the cubes when we were packing. He regretted that decision later lol.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Never travel without them again
reviews.reviewText: These travel cubes are the best things since Orville and Wilbur Wright discovered flight! My daughter told me about these cubes since I travel often. I purchased the turquoise color because that's my vibe. The zippers on these cubes are good quality and the fabric they are made from is breathable and lightweight. I was able to pack several days of clothing into three cubes, two pairs of shoes in one shoe bag(which I love, it is my favorite!), and toiletries into another bag. My husband liked the packing cubes so much that we ran out to a department store to purchase another set for him before we traveled. We spent about $10.00 MORE for his set, they appear to be good quality, but the zippers are smaller and do not slide as easily as the set I purchased on Amazon. I got the best deal and the choice of beautiful colors. Highly recommended for frequent fliers.

As an avid vacationer, I was ALWAYS stuck trying to organize my luggage. After searching for options, I found these packing containers. WOW!!! What a difference. From shirts to pants to anything you want, these containers will organize it all. No fumbling around when you arrive at your destination. Take them out of suitcase and put them in the room drawers, DONE!!. Highly recommended 10/10
